# Editor Cabinet & Collections

## Settings storage
- **Path:** `apps/app/src/shared/collections`
- **Retrieval:** `getCollection(collectionName, role)` from `apps/app/src/shared/collections/getCollection.ts`

## Role-specific config (non-Administrator)
- Stored in `settings` table, attribute `role_schema_{roleName}` (e.g. `role_schema_Editor`)
- Service: `RoleCollectionSchemaService` in `apps/app/src/shared/services/role-collection-schema.service.ts`
- `getCollectionsForRole(roleName)` — list of collection names for role
- `getCollectionConfigForRole(roleName, collectionName)` — collection instance with role overrides (__title, __defaultSort, etc.)

## Editor cabinet (/e/)
- Layout: `apps/app/src/app/(private)/e/layout.tsx`
- Pages: `/e` (list), `/e/deals/[daid]` (detail)
- Sidebar: uses `AppSidebar` from `blocks-app/admin/app-sidebar`
- Base path for Editor: `/e` (links: `/e?c=deals`)
- APIs: `/api/admin/collections`, `/api/admin/state` — must allow Editor role (withEditorGuard)
